rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0001
rows.name: Sorry to keep you waiting, everyone.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0004
rows.name: Mostly he was just talking with Hikari-chan.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0005
rows.name: They knew each other before, right?

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0009
rows.name:
You must be tired after today's events,
so please rest here another night.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0010
rows.name:
She may have a point...
All we really did was talk to His Holiness
Marveni, but I feel quite worn out.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0011
rows.name: Let's take them up on that offer.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0012
rows.name: Yeah, sounds like a good plan.

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0013
rows.name:
Tora not object! Want to sleep on
fluffy-puffy bed every night!

rows.label: fev05_320_125_msg0014
rows.name: Then let's return to the cathedral.
